  "title": "Campaign & Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p>🌟 Thrive Organisation is looking for passionate individuals to be the face and voice of our renowned client brands, creating memorable experiences and achieving collective goals.</p><p>⭐️ We are looking for people who bring the energy! Say goodbye to a dull desk job and hello to a dynamic role where every day is a new adventure and a chance to shine.</p><p>🌈 What is in it for YOU:</p><p>- Overseas incentive trips for top performers</p><p>- A fun, supportive, and high-energy team culture</p><p>- Comprehensive skills training and workshops</p><p>- Clear career progression into leadership roles</p><p>🌈 What your day to day looks like:</p><p>- Engage and excite customers at roadshows, events, and pop-ups</p><p>- Collaborate with a motivated team to hit exciting targets</p><p>- Learn and apply effective marketing and sales techniques</p><p>🌈 What do we want from you?</p><p>- No prior experience needed—full training is provided!</p><p>- An outgoing, positive, and can-do attitude</p><p>- A genuine desire to learn, grow, and succeed with a team</p><p>#WhyThrive #ReadyToThrive</p><p>Ready to launch your career? Apply now and let's grow together!</p>",
